@startuml
[*] --> PowerOnCheck
PowerOnCheck --> [*] : problem detected
PowerOnCheck --> ReadyToUse : everything fine
ReadyToUse --> Reset : reset
ReadyToUse --> Activate : activate
ReadyToUse --> TurnOff : turn off
ReadyToUse --> Monitoring : activated
Monitoring --> Alarm : sensor triggered
Monitoring --> Monitoring : false alarm or time ends
Monitoring --> [*] : password entered
@enduml
